**Component Responsibilities:**
| File | Responsibility |
|------|----------------|
| `utinni_advertise.cpp` | Defines `s_engineHookPoints[]`, the PMF union helper, ctor thunks, 
`GetEngineHookPoints()`, the coverage self-check |
